# Design System

This project uses a consistent design system based on Tailwind CSS and Shadcn UI.

## Styling Approach

- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts): Tailwind configuration with custom theme extensions
- Styling is done exclusively with Tailwind classes
- No CSS modules or separate stylesheets are used

## Theme Configuration

The theme supports both light and dark modes with custom color variables:

- Primary colors: Used for primary actions and brand elements
- Secondary colors: Used for secondary actions and UI elements
- Accent colors: Used for highlighting and special UI elements
- Background/foreground pairs: Used for content areas

## UI Components

The UI components are built on Radix UI primitives with Tailwind styling:

- [components/ui/button.tsx](mdc:components/ui/button.tsx): Button variants (primary, secondary, ghost, etc.)
- [components/ui/card.tsx](mdc:components/ui/card.tsx): Card components for content containers
- [components/ui/dialog.tsx](mdc:components/ui/dialog.tsx): Modal dialogs

## Animation

Animation is provided through Tailwind CSS + Framer Motion:

- CSS animations defined in [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts)
- Complex animations use Framer Motion for smoother transitions
